      <content><![CDATA[<p>The example focuses on several OpenCms features used in combination. These are:</p>
<ul>
<li>The&nbsp;<a href="%(link0)">DisplayTypeSelectWidget</a> for chosing formatters for the list content</li>
<li>The tag <code>&lt;cms:search&gt;</code> to select content</li>
<li>The tag <code>&lt;cms:display&gt;</code> to edit content and create new contents</li>
<li>The tag <code>&lt;cms:edit&gt;</code> to allow content creation when the list is empty</li>
</ul>]]></content>
